name: Vale de Açor, Mértola
comments: Scattered hoard of more than 91 coins, mostly Almoravid and Taifa; the one transitional dinar may not be genuinely associated with the later coins.

comments: Hoard originally contained at least 200 coins; partially dispersed before recording.

comments: Hoard originally contained at least 200 coins; partially dispersed before recording.

name: province of Alacant
